name: Aeroblast
effect:
Wind Based. Inflicts Wounds 
 At Silver Rank, increase this move's power to 4.
 At Gold Rank, this move gains high critical and changes it's accuracy stat to Special.
 At Platinum Rank, increase this move's power to 6.
 At Diamond Rank, this move inflicts frostbite.
description: The victim is trapped in a violently swirling vortex. The strong wind currents make debris fly everywhere.
